    function getMult(ind,s,e,ne,xe,type){
        var easer = bez.getEasingCurve(ne/100,0,1-xe/100,1);
        var mult = 0;
        if(type == 2){
            if(e === s){
                mult = ind >= e ? 1 : 0;
            }else{
                mult = Math.max(0,Math.min(0.5/(e-s) + (ind-s)/(e-s),1));
            }
            mult = easer('',mult,0,1,1);
        }else if(type == 3){
            if(e === s){
                mult = ind >= e ? 0 : 1;
            }else{
                mult = 1 - Math.max(0,Math.min(0.5/(e-s) + (ind-s)/(e-s),1));
            }
 
            mult = easer('',mult,0,1,1);
        }else if(type == 4){
            if(e === s){
                mult = ind >= e ? 0 : 1;
            }else{
                mult = Math.max(0,Math.min(0.5/(e-s) + (ind-s)/(e-s),1));
                if(mult<.5){
                    mult *= 2;
                }else{
                    mult = 1 - mult;
                }
            }
        }else {
            if(ind >= Math.floor(s)){
                if(ind-s < 0){
                    mult = 1 - (s - ind);
                }else{
                    mult = Math.max(0,Math.min(e-ind,1));
                }
            }
        }
        return mult;
    }

        this.o = o;

        this.fc = fc;
        this.m = m;
        this.props = p;
    }
